        "rendered": "Using the Checkbox Field"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "<h2>Basic Setup</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a new Field Group</li>\n<li>Add a Checkbox field</li>\n<li>Configure options:\n<ul>\n<li>Add checkbox choices</li>\n<li>Set layout (vertical/horizontal)</li>\n<li>Choose return format</li>\n<li>Enable/disable &#8220;Select All&#8221;</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Common Use Cases</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Multiple Selection Lists\n<ul>\n<li>Categories/Tags</li>\n<li>Feature toggles</li>\n<li>Permission settings</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Option Configuration\n<ul>\n<li>Settings panels</li>\n<li>Display preferences</li>\n<li>Content filters</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Tips</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Group related options together</li>\n<li>Consider using columns for many options</li>\n<li>Provide clear labels</li>\n<li>Use &#8220;Select All&#8221; for long lists</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
